HEADWORD: Signalment
<hw>Sig"nal*ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of
signaling, or of signalizing; hence, description by peculiar,
appropriate, or characteristic marks.</def> <rj><au>Mrs.
Browning.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
